---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout
  titulo="平台工程 · 内部开发者平台"
  descripcion="基于Kubernetes、GitOps和策略即代码构建内部开发者平台。自助式基础设施降低部署摩擦，同时保持运营控制。"
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden" style="background-color: #0A2540;">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-40" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(147,184,255,0.15) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 28px 28px;"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 sm:py-24">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center text-xs font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-6" style="background: rgba(30,111,255,0.15); color: #93b8ff; border: 1px solid rgba(30,111,255,0.3);">
          平台工程
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-5" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
          让开发者提效而非受阻的平台。
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg max-w-2xl" style="color: rgba(147,184,255,0.8);">
          我们构建内部开发者平台，提供标准化部署、自助式基础设施和Kubernetes抽象——赋能开发团队，而非增加障碍。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CAPABILITIES -->
  <section class="bg-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06);">
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: #0A2540;">自助式基础设施</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #64748b;">开发者无需等待运维团队即可自主配置环境和资源。标准化模板和护栏确保一致性与安全性。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06);">
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: #0A2540;">Kubernetes抽象层</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #64748b;">开发者无需成为Kubernetes专家即可部署应用。Helm chart和Kustomize overlay将集群配置复杂性隐藏于背后。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06);">
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: #0A2540;">标准化部署流程</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #64748b;">跨团队和服务的统一部署流程。黄金路径在保留灵活性的同时强制执行最佳实践。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06);">
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: #0A2540;">ArgoCD与GitOps工作流</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #64748b;">通过ArgoCD管理平台变更。开发者通过PR提交基础设施变更——无需直接访问集群。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06);">
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: #0A2540;">开发者入职</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #64748b;">新开发者在数小时内而非数周内即可上手。有据可查的工作流、本地开发环境和清晰的所有权模型。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06);">
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: #0A2540;">成本优化与治理</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #64748b;">资源标记、预算告警和未使用环境的自动清理。按团队和服务维度的云成本可见性。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section style="background: #0A2540;" class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">构建您的内部开发者平台。</h2>
      <p class="text-base mb-8" style="color: rgba(147,184,255,0.8);">我们从开发者体验审计开始，制定平台路线图。</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-xl font-semibold text-white" style="background: #1E6FFF;">
        联系我们
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
